cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

The paper proposes a method for vision-based driving using imitation learning and high-level command input. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV) as the paper deals with visual input. The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) as it evaluates the proposed method on a robotic truck. Machine learning (cs.LG) is also a likely category as the paper uses imitation learning to train the driving policy. Artificial intelligence (cs.AI) is another possible category as the paper deals with autonomous driving. Finally, control systems (cs.SY) is a possible category as the paper involves controlling the vehicle's movements based on high-level commands.
